Here are 10 User Story Requirements for the WorkflowManager
__________________________________________________________
Identifier    |  User Story
__________________________________________________________
REQ-1.        |  As a user I put an assignment on a calander.
REQ-2.        |  As a user, I can create a project.
REQ-3.        |  As a project leader, I can break a project down into smaller steps.
REQ-4.        |  As a project leader, I can assign project members to different project steps.
REQ-5.        |  As a project leader, I can assign due dates for project steps.
REQ-6.        |  As a user, I can view the assigned steps and due dates.
REQ-7.        |  As a project leader, I can lock project steps from project members.
REQ-8.        |  As a user, I can view the status of my assigned projects.
REQ-9.        |  As a user, I can view dependencies within the project pipeline.
REQ-10.       |  As a user, I can select my profile so the system can determine my roles and permissions.
